screen: C-a S = split screen
screen: C-a [tab] = change focus of screen
screen: C-a X = kill the current region (no-op if there is only one region)
screen: resize +N       increase current region height by N
screen: resize -N       decrease current region height by N
screen: resize  N       set current region height to N
screen: resize  =       make all windows equally high
screen: resize  max     maximize current region height
screen: resize  min     minimize current region height
irssi: /rmreconns Means that if a server is not responding, you can stop irssi trying to connect to it.
svn: svn co svn+ssh://mrled@mrled.org/home/.arietty/mrled/svn/dhd
dpkg: run "apt-get clean" to clear out the large /sw/var/cache directory
dpkg: "apt-get update" resyncs package index
dpkg: "apt-get dist-upgrade" (fink update-all) updates all installed packages. 
cdrecord: mac os x, for combo or super drives, dev=IODVDServices (/0?)mac os x: hdiutil convert /path/to/filename.dmg -format UDTO -o /path/to/savefile.iso
